==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Enrichment
<hw>En*rich"ment</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act of making
rich, or that which enriches; increase of value by improvements,
embellishment, etc.; decoration; embellishment.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Enridge</ent>⟦br⟧
